The Beatles last days in Melbourne before heading off to Sydney. Finally the complete John Lennon interview along with the most complete footage of their 2nd balcony appearance with some upgraded color footage! All these clips are longer! Plus THE BEST Festival Hall concert footage - after sorting out many versions , this one from The Channel 9 Master takes the cake - close to Antholgy quality! This is the best - if you got "Sing for Shell" you will want this - quality, sound, etc makes that look 4 generations less! 100 minutes - in chapters!
